1958;;Buchanan Rides Alone;;American;;Budd Boetticher;;Randolph Scott, Craig Stevens, Jennifer Holden;;western;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Buchanan_Rides_Alone;;On his way home from Mexico to West Texas, Tom Buchanan (Randolph Scott) rides into the Californian border town of Agry, and into a feud between several members of the Agry family. In helping out a Mexican seeking revenge on one of them, Buchanan finds himself against the whole family.[1]